
README for obmenu-generation


INSTALL


  Copy default schema to your home config dir:

  $ cp /usr/etc/xdg/obmenu-generator/schema.pl
~/.config/obmenu-generator/schema.pl


  Edit ~/.config/openbox/menu.xml and put only these contents:

  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
  <openbox_menu xmlns="http://openbox.org/"
   xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
    xsi:schemaLocation="http://openbox.org/">
      <menu id="root-menu" label="obmenu-generator" execute="/usr/bin/obmenu-generator" />
  </openbox_menu>
